Emzy, son of Nigerian billionaire who recently got married to teen actress, Regina Daniels, has taken to his Instagram page to share a screenshot of chat between him and his father’s new wife, Regina Daniels, as they go at loggerheads. In the chat screenshot uploaded by Emzy, Regina Daniels who is now his stepmother, threatened to ensure he (Emzy) will no longer have access to his father. Emzy however responded that he is not afraid of her threats. See screenshot below; The drama is not over between the two who have been at each other’s throat for long. Recall that sometimes ago, Emzy alleged that the actress was using voodoo on his father.